{"tid":210492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【嚴正聲明】《蘋果動新聞》並無合辦活動致電讀者出席","createTime":"2017-04-21T03:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T03:57:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4fe65962890ce6043cb572c6532d7c48a5091585","tid":210492,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:44:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19997034&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19997034%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170421&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNntr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=63604d99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19997034%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170421&h=15674c5a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19997034&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170421</a><br />\n<br />\n【嚴正聲明】<br />\n《蘋果動新聞》並無合辦活動致電讀者出席<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n澄清聲明 ：<br />\n《蘋果動新聞》發現近月有人利用本公司的名義致電讀者，聲稱讀者已獲選為幸運兒，可參與一項與《蘋果動新聞》合辦的活動，出席後更有機會獲取豐富禮品。<br />\n本公司特此聲明澄清，本公司並無舉辦類似合辦活動，不會送出泰國機票連五星級酒店住宿的獎品，有關活動與本公司並無任何關係。<br />\n聲明人：《蘋果動新聞》"},{"pid":"5c6cc89216e0427b89cc63449d5bcccf30161ef3","tid":210492,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"有無人知邊咩事 ?"},{"pid":"fc4015da9e25e4f03c57682c3cc3134b752906a8","tid":210492,"uid":63462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人知邊咩事 ?</blockquote><br />\n你都唔知邊個知"},{"pid":"e796aa32274b1eb888e2034badb4740b35d5a582","tid":210492,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:50:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無人知邊咩事 ?</blockquote><br />\n你